spring core 
_______________ USING SETTER INJECTION/(property injection)___________________________________________________________________________

pom.xml ---<dependencies>--- add spring context and spring core(both of the same version
create Bean(pojo class) ----go to source--- use getter setter
                                            generate contructor setttr fields  
                                            genertae default constructor
                                            generate toString method --if u dont use this it it will give refrence value not the required value
                                            
create config.xml file -------- for bean class -- add property value etc

main method --- create object with the help of xml file...........ApplicationContext c= new ClassPathApplicationContext("xyz.xml");
